snippet.title: CellStrat
snippet.description:
CellStrat is a leading AI Research and Development startup and runs CellStrat AI Lab - a research group which conducts world - class R&D in advanced Computer Vision, Natural Language Processing and Reinforcement learning etc. Currently, we are focused on candidate training and internships in advanced AI, producing world-class research as well as developing cutting - edge AI products. This channel hosts webinar videos of experts who present sessions as part of their research in AI, product development activities and skilling initiatives.

Videos hosted cover entire range of difficulty levels of various courses right from Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Reinforcement Learning, Natural Language Processing, Graph Neural Networks, Artificial General Intelligence and many more...
